Package org.greatage.ioc.symbol

This package represents all classes for working with symbol configuration.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
SymbolProvider This class represents configuration point of SymbolSource and it produces symbol values by their names.
SymbolSource This interface represents an service that obtains string values by their names.
 

Class Summary
DefaultSymbolProvider This class represents configurable SymbolProvider implementation that gets symbols from configured map.
SymbolSourceImpl This class represents default SymbolSource implementation that obtains string values by their names.
SystemSymbolProvider This class represents SymbolProvider implementation that provides system properties as symbols for SymbolSource.
 

Package org.greatage.ioc.symbol Description

This package represents all classes for working with symbol configuration.
